'''2013年馬利國會選舉'''是於2013年11月24日及12月15日舉行的選舉，藉此選出下一屆的[[马里|马里]]國會議員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/98736 |title=Mali Calls Parliamentary Elections for November 24 — Naharnet |publisher=Naharnet.com |date=2013-09-18 |accessdate=2013-11-25 |archive-date=2020-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906182949/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/98736 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此次選舉原先曾預定於2012年6月1日及6月22日舉辦<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mherrera.org/elections.htm |title=Electoral Calendar - international elections world elections |accessdate=2011-05-12 |publisher= |archive-date=2011-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110526192300/http://www.mherrera.org/elections.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但因為國內發生了{{link-en|2012年馬利政變|2012 Malian coup d'état}}與{{link-en|2012年圖阿雷格叛亂|Tuareg rebellion (2012)}}而被迫中止。2013年7月，馬利進行總統大選，但仍傳出槍手於選舉前綁架兩名選舉官員的消息<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-23392819|title=Mali officials abducted ahead of presidential vote|work=BBC News|date=2013-07-20|accessdate=2013-07-20|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111194229/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-23392819|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

第一輪投票未能分出勝負，於是在2013年12月15日舉行第二輪投票<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dw.de/mali-parliamentary-elections-inconclusive-headed-for-second-round/a-17258840 |title=Mali parliamentary elections inconclusive, headed for second round | News | DW.DE | 28.11.2013 |publisher=DW.DE |date=2013-08-14 |accessdate=2013-11-30 |archive-date=2014-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140216095142/http://www.dw.de/mali-parliamentary-elections-inconclusive-headed-for-second-round/a-17258840 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最終選舉結果由[[馬里總統|總統]][[伊巴拉辛·博巴卡·凱塔|伊巴拉辛·博巴卡·凱塔]]所屬的政黨{{link-en|馬利團結黨|Rally for Mali}}獲得147個國會席位中的115個而勝利。{{link-en|索馬伊拉·西塞|Soumaïla Cissé}}帶領的{{link-en|共和民主聯盟|Union for the Republic and Democracy}}則取下18個席位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-25426141|title=Mali President's party wins Parliamentary election|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=2013-12-18|accessdate=2013-12-18|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117213951/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-25426141|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
=== 日期 ===
由於[[法國軍隊|法國軍隊]]當時進駐馬利，協助該國對抗[[阿扎瓦德|阿扎瓦德]]的叛亂份子，[[法國外交部|法國外交部長]][[洛朗·法比尤斯|洛朗·法比尤斯]]表示法軍駐馬利人數到時將會減半，而選舉如期舉行<ref>[http://www.aljazeera.com/news/europe/2013/04/20134652938172937.html France urges Mali to stick to election date] {{Wayback|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/europe/2013/04/20134652938172937.html |date=20200906200428 }} Al Jazeera, 2013-04-06</ref>。[[馬里總理|馬里總理]]{{tsl|en|Django Sissoko|迪昂戈·西索科}}則於2013年4月時造訪北部的高衝突城市[[加奧|加奧]]，宣示選舉訂在7月進行，並已經開始籌備相關事宜。但也有分析家認為拙劣的選舉可能會帶來進一步的動亂<ref>[http://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2013/04/201341264338905806.html Mali leader promises elections in July] {{Wayback|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2013/04/201341264338905806.html |date=20200906200240 }} Al Jazeera, 2013-04-12</ref>。此後，才終於確定國會選舉的日期將是總統大選的幾個月後<ref>{{cite web |author=2013-07-29 |url=http://www.iri.org/news-events-press-center/news/largely-peaceful-process-defines-presidential-election-day-mali |title=Largely Peaceful Process Defines Presidential Election Day in Mali |publisher=IRI |date=2013-07-29 |accessdate=2013-11-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202225345/http://www.iri.org/news-events-press-center/news/largely-peaceful-process-defines-presidential-election-day-mali |archivedate=2013-12-02 }}</ref>。12月15日，展開第二輪選舉<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/15/us-mali-election-idUSBRE9BE0G720131215 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-12-21 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924191744/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/15/us-mali-election-idUSBRE9BE0G720131215 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 事故 ==
12月13日，兩名隸屬於聯合國MINUSMA的[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]]維和人員，在[[基達爾|基達爾]]的{{link-en|馬利團結銀行|Malian Solidarity Bank}}前被炸死，使得兩天後即將舉辦的選舉蒙上陰影<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2013/12/car-bomb-kills-2-un-peacekeepers-mali-20131214144813908884.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-12-15 |archive-date=2014-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140923185124/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2013/12/car-bomb-kills-2-un-peacekeepers-mali-20131214144813908884.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

